From: STGR Browser Team <dev@stgr-browser.dev>
Date: Tue, 2 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: Vertical Tabs sidebar implementation

Implements optional vertical tab layout with:
- Toggle between horizontal (default) and vertical layout
- Left sidebar with tab list showing favicon, title, close, mute, pinned indicators
- Pinned tabs section at top, separated by a subtle divider
- Smooth scroll for many tabs
- Tab preview on hover
- Drag-and-drop reorder with drop indicators
- Tab group nesting with visual hierarchy
- Context menu integration (close, mute, pin, duplicate, bookmark)
- Keyboard shortcut (Ctrl+Shift+E) to toggle
- Toolbar button to toggle
- Animated expand/collapse transition
- Persists preference across sessions
- RTL-aware (uses logical CSS properties)
- Container tab color indicators
- Observer lifecycle management (no leaks)
- Widget registration guard (no duplicate registration)

